data.description: This exceptional residence features four bedrooms and three and a half baths, occupying a generous 3,490 square feet strategically situated on the 3rd fairway. The master suite on the lower level provides both convenience and opulence, while the sunroom and screened porch offer serene spaces to appreciate the scenic surroundings.Elevating the living space's elegance is a double-sided fireplace, complemented by top-of-the-line appliances in the kitchen. The property is equipped with an irrigation system and carefully positioned landscape lighting, enhancing both functionality and aesthetics. Crafted by Scheper Customs Homes, a leading builder in New Bern, this home stands as a testament to superior construction quality.The property includes a large garage, 30'x21', with room to park two vehicles, a golf cart, with seperate golf cart access door, and still have space for a work area. Adding versatility, the spacious bonus room offers ample space for a home office or creative pursuits. The array of features in this home is extensive and goes beyond a mere description--witnessing its charm in person is essential. Discover for yourself the exceptional offerings that set this residence apart.
